<style type="text/css">

    .form-container, .form-body {

        background-image: url("https://properly.com.my/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Savio-Facade-scaled-1.jpg");

        background-size: 1700px 900px; /* This sets the width and height */

        background-repeat: no-repeat; /* Prevents the image from repeating if it's smaller than the container */

    }

    body {

        background-image: url("https://properly.com.my/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Savio-Facade-scaled-1.jpg");

        background-size: 1700px 900px; /* This sets the width and height */

        background-repeat: no-repeat; /* Prevents the image from repeating if it's smaller than the body */

    }

</style>
